comments: Bryant (WAS) firms up in Temple's (CHI) path and absorbs the the contact.
Young (CHI) makes contact to Beal's (WAS) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Bryant (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact during the driving shot attempt by LaVine (CHI) as Beal (WAS) cleanly blocks the shot.
During the inbound, Young (CHI) and Bryant (WAS) engage and disengage off-ball.
During the screen, Beal (WAS) and LaVine (CHI) engage and disengage off-ball.
There is no clear and conclusive angle to see if Beal (WAS) makes contact to LaVine's (CHI) off-arm during his jump shot attempt.
During the drive, Young (CHI) makes clean ball contact to dislodge it from Beal (WAS) and Beal is able to regain control of the ball while staying in-bounds.
Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Temple's (CHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
During the screen, Beal's (WAS) arm is extended forward when marginal contact occurs with LaVine's (CHI) front off-ball.
Young (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Beal's (WAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Young (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Neto's (WAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bryant (WAS) jumps towards White (CHI) and makes contact to his body that dislodges him from his legally obtained position.
During the drive, Young (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position on Beal (WAS) and makes clean ball contact on his dislodge attempt.
LaVine (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Westbrook (WAS) and cleanly blocks the shot.
During the pick, Young (CHI) slightly extends his arms and marginal contact occurs to Beal's (WAS) back as he rolls to the basket.
Westbrook (WAS) reaches out to grab the rebound and marginal contact occurs to Young's (CHI) shoulder.
In transition, Young (CHI) takes a natural path while running down the floor and any leg to leg contact initiated by Westbrook (WAS) is deemed incidental.
White (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Beal (WAS) and Beal fumbles the ball during his shooting motion.
Beal (WAS) commits a take foul on Porter Jr. (CHI).
During the screen, Porter Jr. (CHI) and Bertans (WAS) engage and disengage off-ball and the contact is marginal.
Neto (WAS) releases his inbound pass within 5 seconds.
Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Porter Jr.'s (CHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LaVine (CHI) grabs and holds Westbrook's (WAS) arm during the rebound.
Westbrook (WAS) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
Young (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position off-ball as Bryant (WAS) can't retrieve the errant inbound pass.
